{
  "title": "Evidoc Homepage",
  "type": "page",
  "version": "0.4",
  "page_settings": [],
  "content": [
    {
      "id": "ev_hero01",
      "elType": "container",
      "isInner": false,
      "settings": {
        "content_width": "boxed",
        "flex_direction": "column",
        "background_background": "classic"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "ev_hero02",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "html",
          "isInner": false,
          "settings": {
            "html": "\n<section class=\"py-20 md:py-32 bg-white\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-6 text-center max-w-4xl\">\n    <h6 class=\"text-sm font-semibold text-blue-600 uppercase tracking-wider mb-4\">Introducing Evidoc</h6>\n    <h1 class=\"text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold text-gray-900 leading-tight\">\n      Ask Your Documents.<br>Trust Every Answer.\n    </h1>\n    <p class=\"mt-6 text-lg md:text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">\n      AI-powered document intelligence that retrieves answers from your files — with every claim linked to the exact source sentence. Highlighted, clickable, verifiable.\n    </p>\n    <p class=\"mt-4 text-base text-gray-500 italic\">\n      Not \"it's probably on page 12.\" The actual sentence. The actual words.\n    </p>\n    <div class=\"mt-8\">\n      <a href=\"/contact-us/\" class=\"inline-block px-8 py-3 bg-blue-600 text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors text-lg\">\n        Request Early Access\n      </a>\n    </div>\n    <p class=\"mt-4 text-sm text-gray-400\">15+ document formats · 13 languages · Enterprise-grade security</p>\n  </div>\n</section>\n"
          },
          "elements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ev_prob01",
      "elType": "container",
      "isInner": false,
      "settings": {
        "content_width": "boxed",
        "flex_direction": "column",
        "background_background": "classic"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "ev_prob02",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "html",
          "isInner": false,
          "settings": {
            "html": "\n<section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 bg-white\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\">\n    <div class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900\">Why Today's Document AI Falls Short</h2>\n      <p class=\"mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600\">\n        Your team spends days cross-referencing documents. The mistakes they catch are luck. The ones they miss are liability.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 max-w-5xl mx-auto\">\n      <div class=\"bg-gray-50/70 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200 shadow-sm\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Standard AI Chat + PDF</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-2 text-gray-600\">These tools summarize single files but can't truly understand or cross-reference your documents.</p>\n        <ul class=\"mt-6 space-y-4\">\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\" /></svg>\n            <span><strong class=\"text-gray-700\">Single file only:</strong> Can't answer questions across multiple documents.</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\" /></svg>\n            <span><strong class=\"text-gray-700\">Generates answers:</strong> Text is fabricated, not retrieved. Hallucinations are undetectable.</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-red-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M6 18L18 6M6 6l12 12\" /></svg>\n            <span><strong class=\"text-gray-700\">No real citations:</strong> \"Page 12\" at best — no way to click and verify.</span>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl border-2 border-blue-600 shadow-xl ring-4 ring-blue-600/10\">\n        <h3 class=\"text-xl font-semibold text-blue-700\">Evidoc</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-2 text-gray-600\">Evidoc reads across all your documents, connects the dots, and shows its work — every answer traceable to the source.</p>\n        <ul class=\"mt-6 space-y-4\">\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5\" /></svg>\n            <span><strong class=\"text-gray-700\">Cross-document Q&A:</strong> Ask one question across all your files. Get one verified answer.</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5\" /></svg>\n            <span><strong class=\"text-gray-700\">Retrieves, never fabricates:</strong> Answers extracted from your documents, not generated.</span>\n          </li>\n          <li class=\"flex items-start\">\n            <svg class=\"w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-3 flex-shrink-0 mt-1\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M4.5 12.75l6 6 9-13.5\" /></svg>\n            <span><strong class=\"text-gray-700\">Click-to-verify:</strong> Every citation links to the exact sentence, highlighted on the original page.</span>\n          </li>\n        </ul>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n"
          },
          "elements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ev_feat01",
      "elType": "container",
      "isInner": false,
      "settings": {
        "content_width": "boxed",
        "flex_direction": "column",
        "background_background": "classic"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "ev_feat02",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "html",
          "isInner": false,
          "settings": {
            "html": "\n<section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 bg-gray-50\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\">\n    <div class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900\">Document Intelligence You Can Trust</h2>\n      <p class=\"mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600\">\n        Evidoc builds a Knowledge Graph across your documents — connecting entities, facts, and relationships to deliver verifiable answers.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n      <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100\">\n        <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\" /></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Deterministic Answers</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-2 text-gray-600\">Every answer is extracted directly from your documents — not generated. Knowledge Graph technology ensures factual, traceable responses. Zero hallucination you can't verify.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100\">\n        <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M13.19 8.688a4.5 4.5 0 011.242 7.244l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 01-6.364-6.364l1.757-1.757m13.35-.622l1.757-1.757a4.5 4.5 0 00-6.364-6.364l-4.5 4.5a4.5 4.5 0 001.242 7.244\" /></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Click-to-Verify Citations</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-2 text-gray-600\">Every evidence sentence links back to the exact location in the original document. One click — highlighted text on the source page. See exactly where every fact came from.</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"bg-white p-8 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100\">\n        <div class=\"w-12 h-12 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center\">\n          <svg class=\"w-6 h-6\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7.5 21L3 16.5m0 0L7.5 12M3 16.5h13.5m0-13.5L21 7.5m0 0L16.5 12M21 7.5H7.5\" /></svg>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-5 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Knowledge Graph Intelligence</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-2 text-gray-600\">Understands that \"Acme Corp\" on page 3 and \"ACME Corporation\" on page 47 are the same entity. Connects the dots across hundreds of pages automatically.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n"
          },
          "elements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ev_hiw01",
      "elType": "container",
      "isInner": false,
      "settings": {
        "content_width": "boxed",
        "flex_direction": "column",
        "background_background": "classic"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "ev_hiw02",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "html",
          "isInner": false,
          "settings": {
            "html": "\n<section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 bg-white\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\">\n    <div class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900\">How It Works: 3 Steps to Verified Answers</h2>\n      <p class=\"mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600\">\n        From upload to verified insight — in minutes, not days.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mt-20 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-x-8 gap-y-12 max-w-6xl mx-auto\">\n      <div class=\"text-center relative\">\n        <div class=\"relative z-10 w-28 h-28 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto ring-8 ring-white\">\n          <svg class=\"w-12 h-12\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M3 16.5v2.25A2.25 2.25 0 005.25 21h13.5A2.25 2.25 0 0021 18.75V16.5m-13.5-9L12 3m0 0l4.5 4.5M12 3v13.5\" /></svg>\n          <span class=\"absolute -top-3 -right-2 text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-200/80 -z-10\">1</span>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Upload Your Documents</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-2 text-gray-600\">PDFs, Word docs, spreadsheets, presentations, images — 15+ formats supported. Drag, drop, done.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"text-center relative\">\n        <div class=\"relative z-10 w-28 h-28 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto ring-8 ring-white\">\n          <svg class=\"w-12 h-12\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M7.5 21L3 16.5m0 0L7.5 12M3 16.5h13.5m0-13.5L21 7.5m0 0L16.5 12M21 7.5H7.5\" /></svg>\n          <span class=\"absolute -top-3 -right-2 text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-200/80 -z-10\">2</span>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">AI Builds Knowledge Graph</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-2 text-gray-600\">Evidoc extracts entities, relationships, and facts — building a connected Knowledge Graph across all your documents.</p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"text-center relative\">\n        <div class=\"relative z-10 w-28 h-28 bg-blue-100 text-blue-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto ring-8 ring-white\">\n          <svg class=\"w-12 h-12\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\" /></svg>\n          <span class=\"absolute -top-3 -right-2 text-5xl font-extrabold text-blue-200/80 -z-10\">3</span>\n        </div>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-6 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Ask & Verify</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-2 text-gray-600\">Ask questions in your language. Every answer comes with clickable citations — see the exact source text highlighted on the original page.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n"
          },
          "elements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ev_uc01",
      "elType": "container",
      "isInner": false,
      "settings": {
        "content_width": "boxed",
        "flex_direction": "column",
        "background_background": "classic"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "ev_uc02",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "html",
          "isInner": false,
          "settings": {
            "html": "\n<section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 bg-white\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\">\n    <div class=\"text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto\">\n      <h2 class=\"text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900\">Verified Answers for Every Industry</h2>\n      <p class=\"mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600\">\n        The answer is already in your documents. You just couldn't find it — until now.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n      <div class=\"bg-gray-50/70 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200\">\n        <span class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-blue-800 bg-blue-100 rounded-full\">Legal &amp; Contracts</span>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Cross-Document Contract Review</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>The Problem:</strong> \"Which of our 2,000 contracts contain a change-of-control clause?\" Answering this takes 12 paralegals and 6 weeks.\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>Evidoc:</strong> One question across your entire contract portfolio. Every relevant clause, in every document, cited to the exact sentence. Never miss one again.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-gray-50/70 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200\">\n        <span class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-green-800 bg-green-100 rounded-full\">Procurement &amp; Finance</span>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Invoice &amp; Contract Reconciliation</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>The Problem:</strong> Your team processes 500 invoices/month. Last year's audit found $230K in overpayments. Two FTEs do nothing but cross-check.\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>Evidoc:</strong> \"Do these invoices match the contract terms?\" Every discrepancy cited to the exact line in both documents. What took a week takes minutes.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-gray-50/70 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200\">\n        <span class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-purple-800 bg-purple-100 rounded-full\">Compliance &amp; Audit</span>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Instant Audit Readiness</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>The Problem:</strong> Auditor says \"Show me where your policies address data retention.\" You have 40 policy documents across 3 departments. Last time it took 3 days.\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>Evidoc:</strong> Answer in seconds — with the exact policy language highlighted. Not \"we'll get back to you.\" The answer, the source, the proof. Right now.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n      <div class=\"bg-gray-50/70 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200\">\n        <span class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-amber-800 bg-amber-100 rounded-full\">Manufacturing &amp; Quality</span>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Regulatory &amp; SOP Compliance</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>The Problem:</strong> Inspector asks: \"Where does your SOP address cleaning validation for Line 3?\" You have 400 SOPs.\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>Evidoc:</strong> Exact SOP section highlighted in 30 seconds. Gap analysis across your documentation with cited references from both old and new standards.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-gray-50/70 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200\">\n        <span class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-rose-800 bg-rose-100 rounded-full\">Real Estate</span>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Contract Change Detection</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>The Problem:</strong> Buyer's attorney modified the counter-offer. What exactly changed? Does it conflict with the HOA docs? Closing is Friday.\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>Evidoc:</strong> \"What changed?\" — every difference highlighted on the PDF. Cross-reference against HOA docs instantly. Close with confidence.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"bg-gray-50/70 p-8 rounded-2xl border border-gray-200\">\n        <span class=\"inline-block px-3 py-1 text-sm font-medium text-indigo-800 bg-indigo-100 rounded-full\">IP &amp; Patents</span>\n        <h3 class=\"mt-4 text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Prior Art &amp; Portfolio Analysis</h3>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>The Problem:</strong> \"Does this prior art invalidate our claim 3?\" 200 references to check. That's 20 hours of attorney time at $600/hr.\n        </p>\n        <p class=\"mt-3 text-gray-600\">\n          <strong>Evidoc:</strong> Cross-reference hundreds of documents. Every relevant paragraph cited to the exact source. Prior art search: 12 hours → 12 minutes.\n        </p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n"
          },
          "elements": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ev_sec01",
      "elType": "container",
      "isInner": false,
      "settings": {
        "content_width": "boxed",
        "flex_direction": "column",
        "background_background": "classic"
      },
      "elements": [
        {
          "id": "ev_sec02",
          "elType": "widget",
          "widgetType": "html",
          "isInner": false,
          "settings": {
            "html": "\n<section class=\"py-20 md:py-28 bg-gray-50\">\n  <div class=\"container mx-auto px-6\">\n    <h3 class=\"text-center text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900\">Enterprise-Grade Security &amp; Capabilities</h3>\n    <div class=\"mt-8 grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8 text-center max-w-5xl mx-auto\">\n      <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100\">\n        <svg class=\"w-10 h-10 text-blue-600 mx-auto\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M16.5 10.5V6.75a4.5 4.5 0 10-9 0v3.75m-.75 11.25h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25-2.25H6.75a2.25 2.25 0 00-2.25 2.25v6.75a2.25 2.25 0 002.25 2.25z\" /></svg>\n        <h4 class=\"mt-3 font-semibold text-gray-700\">Role-Based Access Control</h4>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100\">\n        <svg class=\"w-10 h-10 text-blue-600 mx-auto\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fill=\"none\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" stroke-width=\"1.5\" stroke=\"currentColor\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" d=\"M18 18.72a9.094 9.094 0 003.741-.479 3 3 0 00-4.682-2.72m.94 3.198l.001.031c0 .225-.012.447-.037.666A11.944 11.944 0 0112 21c-2.17 0-4.207-.576-5.963-1.584A6.062 6.062 0 016 18.719m12 0a5.971 5.971 0 00-.941-3.197m0 0A5.995 5.995 0 0012 12.75a5.995 5.995 0 00-5.058 2.772m0 0a3 3 0 00-4.681 2.72 8.986 8.986 0 003.74.477m.94-3.197a5.971 5.971 0 00-.94 3.197M15 6.75a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0zm-13.5 0a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z\" /></svg>\n        <h4 class=\"mt-3 font-semibold text-gray-700\">Multi-Tenancy</h4>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"bg-white p-6 rounded-2xl shadow-lg border border-gray-100\">\n        <svg class=\"w-10 h-10 text-blue-600 mx-auto\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" fil